1. *Uradim* sve što je potrebno. (I will do everything that is necessary.)
2. Narediću da se *uradi* sve što je potrebno. (I will order that everything that is necessary is done.)
3. *Urađeno* je sve što je trebalo. (Everything that was needed has been done.)
4. Naredio sam da se *uradi* sve što je trebalo. (I ordered that everything that was needed be done.)